data.description: Adorable cottage located in St. Martin Parish.  This one has it all.  3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and flex space that can be used as either additional storage or an office space.  Chef's Kitchen has been recently updated and this home has no carpet.  Outdoors there is a huge covered space for parking that would also make the perfect spot for gatherings.  This home has mature landscaping and a lovely inground pool.  If that isn't enough there is also a workshop!!!  Call quickly for your showing!!
